{"tid":1058360,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"19 fresh grad 有兩個offer, 點揀好","createTime":"2019-03-12T13:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T03:41:23.000Z","uid":96644,"like":16,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"0524a7f13617ac9d7a2a63831000528e067bbd7a","tid":1058360,"uid":96644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:12:01.000Z","msg":"我cs fresh grad，聽講出面話有手有腳就請人，我開頭都唔信，但係我好快就收到兩個offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家唔知點揀好，希望各位巴絲可以俾我意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一份就喺日資(以前唔係,但係之後被日本公司收購) 到做BA，主要係負責同客人傾requirement，然後傾完再同backend傾，人工比第二份好，最高可以有15000一個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於第二份就喺中資到做gt ，間公司係美國跨國企業，不過香港呢邊就交咗俾中國企業負責，咁工作方面就做backend啲野，主要係根據返客人要求砌返啲野咁，但係人工比較低，得10000左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過勝在有得學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋比較有人情味，因為間公司好照顧弱勢社群，可以話係一間佛心慈善企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外順帶一提第一份工，女的數量比男嘅多好多，話唔定好快就有得出pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位覺得我應該點揀好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c65ac0f7d96c70f15df2dd86ee3aac61250edc4","tid":1058360,"uid":26422,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:16:59.000Z","msg":"唔使諗啦話。。。爭五千<br />\n即係50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d72c9f4b91e62b04a2a28ce41c8de232d55a2a","tid":1058360,"uid":46587,"like":97,"dislike":1,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔要<br />\n再揾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37c73535c400db26f9db770367fe307b3d11340","tid":1058360,"uid":32455,"like":11,"dislike":20,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"CS fg 12k，15k嗰份簡直係高薪貴族"},{"pid":"5ca36fd1b91e4dcde821ff6c8d3ecb6f0e1a7c4a","tid":1058360,"uid":33352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"簡第一份再放徦就義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffcfecfd436101565db2d960c8cbba42cee92b8","tid":1058360,"uid":196924,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:28:18.000Z","msg":"間公司好照顧弱勢社群 唔代表會照顧員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effc35d82852cde254ff72d00f9ba23c726b5b7d","tid":1058360,"uid":165482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"A啦"},{"pid":"16348ee7681db7d43d7eb881d2cfb68779748217","tid":1058360,"uid":36295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T14:34:08.000Z","msg":"GT 10000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99ce2929ffdbb859d8695cde330e7f767994995","tid":1058360,"uid":81368,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTi